The museum is open to Members and the public from 9 A.M. to 5 P.M. on Tuesdays, Wednesdays, Thursdays, Fridays and Saturdays. In addition, the
               public exhibition is open on Sundays from 1 to 4 P.M. The museum is closed on Mondays and the following holidays: New Year's Day, Lincoln's Birthday, Washington's Birthday, Memorial Day, Independence Day, Election Day,
               Thanksgiving Day and Christmas Day.
